3545337[=]ustv[=]2097996[=]2008-06-26 00:43:45[=]标题：【号外】GG主角们的最新动态!! 来自Gossip Girl的大爆料!![=]转自 GG中文粉丝网(gossipgirl.5d6d)  翻译&&编辑：Davidding -----http://gossipgirl.5d6d.com/bbs.php  June 19th, 2008 One of my spies in the Hamptons has spotted Serena on the beach every single day of the summer so far. And every day she is wearing a different bathing suit! She has not repeated a swimsuit once! Can you believe that?? Plus Serena’s hair has gotten even lighter and her skin even darker. She looks better than ever. We’re hoping she’s breaking some hearts out there. Girl deserves a fun summer.  迄今为止的每一个夏日,我在汉普顿的眼线都会目击Serena在沙滩上出现,并且每天都身着不同款式的泳衣,你能相信吗?她竟然从未重复穿着过其中任何一件!!!!!! 另外,现在的Serena,秀发越发光泽闪亮,皮肤越发古铜健康,她看起来比从前任何时间都要棒!! 我们由衷希望她能在那好好散散心.女孩应当拥有一个愉快的夏日!!!   June 17th, 2008 Spotted: S and a totally reluctant N at the East Hampton Cinema seeing Sex and the City (no word on whether or not this was a date, did anyone see hand holding? I’m very curious. Anyways, Serena is so Carrie! (and so is Gossip Girl!)  目击:Serena和相当不情不愿的Nate出现在东汉普顿的一家电影院中,观看刚刚全线上映的《欲望城市》(实在不能说这到底算不算是一次约会),有任何人看到他们牵手吗?对此我非常好奇.但不管怎样,Serena看起来棒极了,迷人性感,像极了影片中的Carrie(当然绯闻少女也是如此!!)  D and V at Il Laboratorio del Gelato eating, duh, gelato. D had the fresh mint, V had the hazelnut. A sweaty J rolling a clothing rack down Jane Street. OMG, so embarrassing!  至于D和V相约在Il Laboratorio del Gelato冰淇凌店品尝冷饮,哦,不,是Il Laboratorio del gelato,D点了自己喜欢的鲜薄荷口味,而V选了榛子味. 我们辛苦的小J呢,正在Jane Street进行一次服装大整理,汗流浃背?真是一件令人为难的工作!!  I at T. Fancy buying luggage. I hear she’s spending the summer in Israel visiting Kati. Adorable! BFFAE! P and H at the New York City Ballet’s “Dance with the Dancers”. They were both wearing Salvatore Ferragamo, the event’s sponsor. They looked fab.  I（Isabel，剧中的黑人女孩）正在T. Fancy购买行李包，据说，她将前往以色列拜访她的BFFAE（Best Friends Forever And Ever）Kati,并在那度过这个夏季,好一个值得敬慕的假期!!  P和H(剧中的跟班Penny和Hazel)将会出席纽约市芭蕾舞团主办的“Dance with the Dancers”舞会，身着舞会赞助商Salvatore Ferragamo的服饰，她们看上去美极了!!  B at the Galleria degli Uffizi in Florence with a really hot guy who was totally not C. They were standing pretty close as they checked out Botticelli’s Birth of Venus. Speaking of C, he’s been MIA. Where could he be? Is he on a plane to Tuscany to get to Blair? Or is he getting friendly with random girls in the city and the Hamptons? If you see him please let me know. I’m dying to find out his whereabouts.  而我们的女王B呢?她在佛罗伦萨和一位相当帅气性感的男子一同参观乌菲至兹美术馆. 但可以确定的是这位迷人的男子并不是Chuck。在参观Botticelli的维纳斯诞生时，他们俩靠的相当近，举止亲密。  说到Chuck ，当真不知所终，他会在哪呢？是坐飞机去托斯卡纳区(意大利行政区名)追B了？还是在汉普顿和众多的大胆开放的美女调情？如果你遇见了他，麻烦告诉我一声，我真的很想知道他现在究竟在干什么？   转载请注明出处作者 转自 GG中文粉丝网(gossipgirl.5d6d) http://gossipgirl.5d6d.com/bbs.php
